title: High Protein Dish 17-1
method: Preheat oven to 200°C.
Season chicken with salt, pepper, and optional spices.
Roast chicken for 25 minutes until juices run clear.
Cook quinoa according to packet instructions.
Steam vegetables until tender.
Plate chicken over quinoa with vegetables on the side.
